        "action": "Introduce harsher sentencing for theft and fund increased police presence",
        "additional_details": "We think more police could tackle incidents of public theft with regards to shoplifting and increasing phone theft, ensuring criminals are held accountable for their actions.\r\n \r\nThere has been a rise in people stealing from shops and pickpocketing and we think this has caused local communities to become unsafe.",
        "background": "We think the government should introduce harsher sentencing for theft. We also think more police should be patrolling on our streets.",
